room_title: Escape room "Rivalry" by Challenges East Lansing in Lansing
room_address: 3044 E Lake Lansing Rd, East Lansing, MI 48823
room_description:
One hour until the big game and the rival team has just escaped with your mascot. Can you find your way out of the locker room and bring the spirit back home before the game starts?
There are two identical rooms available at the location, each for 2-6 players, which can be played in competition mode. Your team will then be competing to find the coveted Paul Bunyan trophy before the big game begins.
